nodes.text: The massacre on Suba Tren was an incident that took place on Suba Tren in which a number of Frizznoths were massacred. Vap Tomulus was involved in the massacre, later claiming that he had not murdered the Frizznoths on purpose. The Frizznoth Mozeen Parapa, leader of the Parapa Cartel, tracked down Tomulus and killed him in revenge for the massacre.
